==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-brother-in-law.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[brother]]-[[in-law]]|brothers-in-law}}

# The [[brother]] of one's [[spouse]].
# One's [[sibling]]'s husband.
# The husband of the sibling of one's spouse.

====Quotations====
*'''1597''', [[w:William_Shakespeare|William Shakespeare]], '' Henry IV, Part I'', act 1, sc. 3,
*:We at our own charge shall ransom straight
*:His '''brother-in-law''', the foolish Mortimer;

